'''Americanophobia''' (from Mod L. ''Americanus'', "American" + Greek. ''-φοβία (phobia)'', "fear")  denotes a fear or aversion of [[American people|Americans]] or American culture. This can be contrasted with [[Anti-Americanism]] which denotes an opposition or hostility towards America and/or Americans.

